@startuml 02-tools-integrations
title Tools va Tich hop he thong ngoai - theo tung Agent
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

package "LegalAgent" {
  [business_registry_lookup\n(FunctionTool)] as T1
  [legal_kb_retriever\n(RAG Tool)] as T2
}
[Cong DKKD Quoc gia\n(mock API)] as EXT1
T1 --> EXT1

package "FinancialCreditAgent" {
  [financial_statement_parser\n(FunctionTool, OCR/parse BCTC)] as T3
  [ratio_calculator\n(DSCR, don bay, thanh khoan)] as T4
  [bank_statement_reconciler] as T5
  [financial_kb_retriever\n(RAG Tool)] as T6
}
[Document Store (S3)\nBCTC / to khai thue / sao ke] as EXT2
T3 --> EXT2
T5 --> EXT2

package "CollateralAgent" {
  [secured_transactions_lookup\n(FunctionTool)] as T7
  [collateral_valuation_tool] as T8
  [collateral_kb_retriever\n(RAG Tool)] as T9
}
[Dang ky Giao dich\nBao dam (mock API)] as EXT3
[Du lieu gia thi truong\n(mock / noi bo)] as EXT4
T7 --> EXT3
T8 --> EXT4

package "ScoringAgent" {
  [internal_rating_model\n(scorecard calculator)] as T10
  [scoring_kb_retriever\n(RAG Tool)] as T11
}

package "ComplianceAMLAgent" {
  [cic_lookup\n(mock CIC API)] as T12
  [sanctions_screening\n(fuzzy match)] as T13
  [related_party_exposure_calc] as T14
  [compliance_kb_retriever\n(RAG Tool)] as T15
}
[CIC - Trung tam Thong tin\nTin dung Quoc gia (mock)] as EXT5
[Sanctions/PEP Lists\nOFAC/UN/EU (mock/dataset)] as EXT6
T12 --> EXT5
T13 --> EXT6

package "ReportingAgent" {
  [report_template_filler] as T16
}

note bottom
  O giai doan hackathon/demo: EXT1, EXT3, EXT5, EXT6
  la mock API / dataset gia lap (chua co quyen truy cap
  he thong that cua NHNN/CIC). Thiet ke tool interface
  (function signature) sao cho co the swap sang API that
  sau nay ma khong doi logic Agent.
end note

@enduml
